  "prompt": "Which is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Warren County IL?",
  "response": "Finding a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Warren County, IL, involves considering factors such as treatment programs offered, staff qualifications, facilities, and patient reviews. Here are a few options in the general area:\n\n1. **Bridgeway Inc.** - Located in Galesburg, IL, Bridgeway offers comprehensive substance abuse treatment programs including inpatient rehab. They provide individualized treatment plans, counseling, and support groups.\n\n2. **White Oaks Detox Center** - Located in Peoria, IL, they offer inpatient detox and rehab services with focused care for individuals struggling with addiction.\n\n3. **Rosecrance Health Network** - Situated in nearby Rockford, IL, Rosecrance provides a wide range of substance abuse treatment services including inpatient rehab with personalized care plans and a multidisciplinary approach.\n\n4. **Chestnut Health Systems** - With a facility in Bloomington, IL, Chestnut Health Systems offers a comprehensive inpatient treatment program with a focus on holistic care and recovery support.\n\nRemember to check each center's specific programs, insurance acceptance, and any other criteria that are important for you or your loved one. It\u2019s also advisable to visit the facility or talk to their intake coordinators to get a sense of the environment and offerings.",
